## Installation

### Install this node module
```
npm install git+ssh://git@gitlab.project.com:plugins/ng-rt-nodes-blockchain.git

or install it in node-red module directly under nodes

npm install --prefix ./node_modules/node-red git+ssh://git@gitlab.project.com:plugins/ng-rt-nodes-blockchain.git
